  <title>View files in a list or grid</title>

  <comment>
    <cite date="2012-02-20" href="mailto:yrazes@gmail.com">Julita Inca</cite>
    <p>This assumes the reader knows how to open <app>Documents</app>.
    By the end of this page, the reader will be able to change between list and
    grid format.</p>
  </comment>

  <p>Documents and collections are presented in <gui>Grid</gui> format by
  default. To view in <gui>List</gui> format:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press the list button in the top-right corner of the window.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <note style="info">
    <p>List view has columns displaying the document type and date modified,
    and whether it's stored locally or remotely in one of your online
    accounts.</p>
  </note>

  <p>Click the grid button in the top-right corner of the window to return to
  the grid view.</p>

